    permission before writing to an Amiga-DOS formatted diskette.


  "Backup disk check"

    In the same way as formatted diskettes, Diavolo Backup checks if the
    diskette has been previously used as a backup, and if so, warns you.
    De-selecting this option will prevent Diavolo Backup from informing you
